element.name: dcat:Dataset
element.label: Dataset
element.description: A dataset is a collection of data, published or curated by a single agent. Data comes in many forms including numbers, words, pixels, imagery, sound and other multi-media, and potentially other types, any of which might be collected into a dataset.

element.name: dct:title
element.label: Title
element.description: A name given to the item.

element.name: dct:description
element.label: Description
element.description: A free-text account of the record.

element.name: dct:identifier
element.label: Identifier
element.description: The identifier might be used as part of the URI of the item, but still having it represented explicitly is useful.

element.name: dcat:contactPoint
element.label: Contact point
element.description: Relevant contact information for the cataloged resource.

element.name: dct:issued
element.label: Publication date
element.description: Date of formal issuance (e.g., publication) of the item.

element.name: dct:modified
element.label: Modification date
element.description: Most recent date on which the catalog entry was changed, updated or modified.

element.name: dct:publisher
element.label: Publisher
element.description: The entity responsible for making the item available.

element.name: dct:accessRights
element.label: Access Rights
element.description: Information about who can access the resource or an indication of its security status.

element.name: dct:conformsTo
element.label: Conforms To
element.description: An established standard to which the described resource conforms.

element.name: dct:accrualPeriodicity
element.label: frequency
element.description: The frequency with which items are added to a collection.

element.name: dct:hasVersion
element.label: Has as version
element.description: Complete with a reference (title, identifier, ...) to a dataset that is a version or an edition of your dataset.

element.name: rdf:resource
element.label: Is Version Of
element.description: A related resource of which the described resource is a version, edition, or adaptation.

element.name: dct:isVersionOf
element.label: Is a version of
element.description: Complete with a reference (title, identifier, ...) to a dataset of which your dataset is a version or an edition.

element.name: dcat:landingPage
element.label: Landing page
element.description: A Web page that can be navigated to in a Web browser to gain access to the catalog, a dataset, its distributions and/or additional information.

element.name: dct:language
element.label: Language
element.description: This refers to the natural language used for textual metadata (i.e. titles, descriptions, etc) of a cataloged resource (i.e. dataset or service) or the textual values of a dataset distribution.

element.name: rdf:resource
element.label: Language
element.description: This refers to the natural language used for textual metadata (i.e. titles, descriptions, etc) of a cataloged resource (i.e. dataset or service) or the textual values of a dataset distribution.

element.name: dct:provenance
element.label: provenance
element.description: A statement of any changes in ownership and custody of the resource since itscreation that are significant for its authenticity, integrity andinterpretation.

element.name: dct:relation
element.label: Related dataset
element.description: Complete with a reference (title, identifier, ..) to a related dataset or related source of your dataset.

element.name: dct:source
element.label: Source dataset
element.description: Complete with a reference (title, identifier, ...) to the dataset from which your dataset is derived.

element.name: dct:spatial
element.label: Geographic extent
element.description: The geographical area covered by the dataset.

element.name: dct:issued
element.label: Date Issued
element.description: Date of formal issuance (e.g., publication) of the resource.

element.name: dct:license
element.label: License
element.description: A legal document giving official permission to do something with the resource.
